## Why This Is Asked
Evaluates practical design of end-to-end attestation workflows in multi-tenant environments with integrated policy enforcement and security controls.

## Key Concepts
- Post-deployment tenant-scoped attestations using HSM-based key management
- SBOM integrity verification and runtime hashing for supply chain security
- OPA/Gatekeeper integration for policy validation and traffic gating
- Multi-tenant security isolation with compliance enforcement mechanisms

## Code Example
```javascript
// Sample attestation verification pseudocode
function verifyAttestation(attestation, tenantPolicy) {
  // Validate signature with tenant's HSM public key
  const isValidSignature = crypto.verify(
    attestation.signature,
    attestation.payload,
    tenantPolicy.publicKey
  );

  // Check policy compliance through OPA/Gatekeeper
  const isCompliant = opa.evaluate(
    attestation.payload,
    tenantPolicy.constraints
  );

  return isValidSignature && isCompliant;
}
```

